languages.text: "Мы заключили сделку. Ты обещал помощь, так не вздумай пытаться меня надуть!"
"We made a deal. You promised you would provide help. Do not think of reneging on what we agreed upon!"
languages.original_text: "Мы заключили сделку. Ты обещал помощь, так не вздумай пытаться меня надуть!"

traits.locale_text: "We made a deal. You promised you would provide help. And you will hold up your end of what we agreed upon!"

languages.text: 「我々は取引をしたはずだ。助力をすると、約束したではないか。合意したことを反故にするつもりか！」
languages.original_text: "We made a deal. You promised you would provide help. Do not think of reneging on what we agreed upon!"

traits.locale_text: 「我々は取引をしたはずだ。助力をすると、約束したではないか。合意したことを反故にするつもりか！」

languages.text: “我们已经达成了协议，你也答应过我会帮助我。你别打算违背协议！”
languages.original_text: "We made a deal. You promised you would provide help. Do not think of reneging on what we agreed upon!"

traits.locale_text: “我们已经达成了协议，你也答应过我会帮助我。你别打算违背协议！”

languages.text: « Nous avions un accord. Vous m'avez promis de me venir en aide. Je ne vous laisserai pas revenir sur votre parole ! »
languages.original_text: "We made a deal. You promised you would provide help. Do not think of reneging on what we agreed upon!"

traits.locale_text: « Nous avions un accord. Vous m'avez promis de me venir en aide. Je ne vous laisserai pas revenir sur votre parole ! »

languages.text: «Hemos hecho un trato. Has prometido que ayudarías. ¡Ni se te ocurra renegar de lo pactado!».
languages.original_text: "We made a deal. You promised you would provide help. Do not think of reneging on what we agreed upon!"

traits.locale_text: «Hemos hecho un trato. Has prometido que ayudarías. ¡Ni se te ocurra renegar de lo pactado!».

languages.text: "Wir hatten eine Abmachung. Ihr habt versprochen, Ihr würdet helfen. Denkt nicht einmal daran, unsere Vereinbarung aufzukündigen."
languages.original_text: "We made a deal. You promised you would provide help. Do not think of reneging on what we agreed upon!"

traits.locale_text: "Wir hatten eine Abmachung. Ihr habt versprochen, Ihr würdet helfen. Denkt nicht einmal daran, unsere Vereinbarung aufzukündigen."

languages.text: "Bir anlaşma yaptık. Yardımda bulunacağının sözünü verdin. Sözünden dönmeye kalkma!"
